{"tid":2364084,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"眾議員指控Pelosi : 用國會權力推翻眾議員選舉結果 #StealTheSeat","createTime":"2021-01-12T16:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T06:53:40.000Z","uid":14918,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"95bf431ba8da115fc1c4170859b30132f1d0da80","tid":2364084,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:35:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/repashleyhinson/status/1346878467384737800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frepashleyhinson%2Fstatus%2F1346878467384737800&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEdB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=a571c614\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frepashleyhinson%2Fstatus%2F1346878467384737800&h=7a9b9b33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/repashleyhinson/status/1346878467384737800</a><br />\n<br />\nSource: Iowa 1st選區 (IW01)當選議員Ashley Hinson<br />\n<br />\n牽涉人物: Iowa 2nd 選區 (IW02)<br />\nMariannette Miller-Meeks (MMM) [共和黨]<br />\nvs <br />\nRita Hart[民主黨]<br />\n<br />\n事件來龍去脈(時間排序為descending):<br />\n<br />\n1月 Iowa 1st - Ashley 幫黨友辯護，控訴Pelosi 無權將選擇點票問題放上國會討論或審視，質疑Pelosi要越權推翻IW02選舉結果，違反IW02民意<br />\n控訴主流媒體掩飾此事，所以拍片上Twitter要求關注<br />\n<br />\n1月3 MMM已宣誓出任 IW02 眾議員<br />\n<br />\n12月31 Pelosi 議長發言人Drew Hammill表示Iowa 2nd 選情有爭議，國會<strong>暫時性</strong>畀MMM出任議席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> *1<br />\n而國會方面，由行政委員會決定緊「點搞」。<br />\n<br />\n12月23 Rita Hart 要求國會審查呢6票爭議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> *2<br />\n<br />\n11月25 MMM被修正只以6票領先勝出<br />\nMMM團隊指控重新點票過程用High Speed Machine取代人手點票係非法。*4到最後auditors + canvas board見證宣布MMM勝選<br />\n<br />\n11月12 MMM 出席國會眾議員迎新活動<br />\n同日，Rita Hart要求全部county重新點票<br />\n<br />\n11月10 MMM領先40，因Lucas<br />\n county以clerical error原因修改得票，MMM第二次宣布勝選<br />\n<br />\n11月6 MMM領先162票，因Jasper county以clerical error原因修改得票<br />\n<br />\n11月4 第一次點票，MMM領先282票，MMM宣布勝選，但主流媒體話too close to call拒絕承認<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource go to #2"},{"pid":"d4a57b15d9905a13d8fcefc84d6ba645ba9c1e0f","tid":2364084,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:35:11.000Z","msg":"以下三條係Iowa 1st Rep幫黨友辯護<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/repashleyhinson/status/1347597487935287297\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frepashleyhinson%2Fstatus%2F1347597487935287297&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEdB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=0f608be1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frepashleyhinson%2Fstatus%2F1347597487935287297&h=5af23a00\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/repashleyhinson/status/1347597487935287297</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/repashleyhinson/status/1348999110255378434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frepashleyhinson%2Fstatus%2F1348999110255378434&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEdB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=6a7dac43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frepashleyhinson%2Fstatus%2F1348999110255378434&h=eadc28e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/repashleyhinson/status/1348999110255378434</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/repashleyhinson/status/1347226974981382145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frepashleyhinson%2Fstatus%2F1347226974981382145&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEdB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=ef103c1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frepashleyhinson%2Fstatus%2F1347226974981382145&h=0cea7d95\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/repashleyhinson/status/1347226974981382145</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*1 <a href=\"https://apnews.com/article/election-2020-iowa-mariannette-miller-meeks-elections-iowa-city-b0b8ddb4e878a54fce078ac116e3eb76\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Felection-2020-iowa-mariannette-miller-meeks-elections-iowa-city-b0b8ddb4e878a54fce